author: Cleo Abram
description:
What is 3I/Atlas?? I keep hearing about this ancient alien object speeding toward our Sun… that some scientists say might be “alien technology”...

So I emailed one of the world’s most important astrophysicists, Dr. Alex Filippenko, to learn what’s real.

And no, it WON’T hit us… but there are nearby asteroids that might! We’re working on a story all about Near Earth Objects, so to find out how we protect our planet… subscribe!

#shorts #comet #asteroid #space #alien
title: What Is 3I/Atlas REALLY?
